From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: alina sireneva <alina@tei.su>
Date: Tue, 12 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: Restore hamburger side drawer for old layout mode

Adds inu_-prefixed drawer slide/gesture/scrim mechanism back to
DrawerLayoutContainer, wires it from LaunchActivity (via DrawerHelper)
and DialogsActivity (MenuDrawable hamburger, back-press close).

---
 .../ui/ActionBar/DrawerLayoutContainer.java   | 195 +++++++++++++++++-
 .../java/org/telegram/ui/DialogsActivity.java |  30 ++-
 .../java/org/telegram/ui/LaunchActivity.java  |  10 +
 3 files changed, 230 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

